423
00:48:47,199 --> 00:48:52,139
[SPEAKER_01] Od Rimca, od Infobip-a, od, ne znam, Nadobita.

424
00:48:52,139 --> 00:48:53,400
[SPEAKER_01] Tako ima ih cvanj sila da.

425
00:48:53,400 --> 00:49:04,199
